<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Flor de Lótus | Pureza e Resiliência</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar" role="navigation" aria-label="Menu Principal">
            <div class="logo">Lótus<span>Essence</span></div>
            <div class="acc-controls">
                <button onclick="changeFontSize(1)" aria-label="Aumentar fonte">A+</button>
                <button onclick="changeFontSize(-1)" aria-label="Diminuir fonte">A-</button>
                <button onclick="toggleContrast()" id="contrast-toggle" aria-label="Alternar Alto Contraste">◐</button>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero reveal" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 id="hero-title">A Flor que Floresce no Lodo</h1>
                <p>Simbolizando pureza espiritual, a lótus nos ensina sobre superação e beleza.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="gallery-section" class="container reveal">
            <h2>Variedades de Lótus</h2>
            <div id="lotus-grid" class="grid-container" role="region" aria-live="polite">
                </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container reveal">
            <h2>Simbolismo e Significado</h2>
            <div id="faq-container" class="expandable-list">
                </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer role="contentinfo">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Flor de Lótus - Design Inclusivo.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
